  this is a stupid little hack that displays a pomodoro timer in the
  corner of yr screen with dzen2.

  read the options in the head of pomodzen.py to configure to yr own
  tastes.

  run by:

	$ python pomodzen.py

  or

	$ ./pomodzen.py

  be sure to check the cmdline options out:

	$ ./pomodzen.py --help

  you will need: dzen2 and python. tested with py2.7 and py3.2 so i
  guess everything's copacetic there but hey ymmv homie.

  feedback and party invitations to wrl@illest.net danke
